snippet.title: 9 to 5 Smash It  - Mobile Game Trailer
snippet.description:
9 to 5 Smash It is a fast paced mobile game available in the Google Play Store. Work your way to the top at ZaamCore Enterprises by smashing the competition! Punch your mechanical coworkers by pushing your phone forward. The faster you move your phone, the harder you punch. Climb the corporate ladder in 9 to 5 Smash It!

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.RasCom.SmashIt
